  "code": "flowchart LR\n    %% Instead of flowchart one can also use graph!\n    %% Possible FlowChart orientations are:\n    %% TB - Top to bottom\n    %% TD - Top-down/ same as top to bottom\n    %% BT - Bottom to top\n    %% RL - Right to left\n    %% LR - Left to right\n    Box01 --> Box02\n    Box02 --- Box03\n    Box01 -.-> Box04\n    Box04 ~~~ Box05\n",
  "diagram_type": "flowchart size:250..400",
  "collected_at": "2026-02-27T03:34:42.547798",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示五个盒子之间的各种连接关系。方向我想用从左到右的，这样阅读起来比较自然。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Box01",
        "Box02",
        "Box03",
        "Box04",
        "Box05",
        "LR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，从左到右布局。那这五个盒子之间的连线类型有要求吗？比如实线、虚线，或者不同的箭头样式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Box01",
        "Box02",
        "Box03",
        "Box04",
        "Box05"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Box01到Box02用带箭头的实线，表示直接流程。Box02到Box03用普通实线，没有箭头。Box01还要连到Box04，用虚线表示间接关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Box01",
        "Box02",
        "Box03",
        "Box04"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我先把这三条连线加上：Box01箭头指向Box02，Box02实线连接Box03，Box01虚线连接Box04。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Box01",
        "Box02",
        "Box03",
        "Box04"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对了，Box04和Box05之间我想用一种特殊的连接，就是视觉上把它们分开，但又表示它们在同一组，用那种隐形连线吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Box04",
        "Box05"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "隐形连线对吧，就是让Box04和Box05在布局上靠近，但中间不显示任何线条。这样Box05就通过Box04间接和整个图关联起来了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Box04",
        "Box05"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这样。整个图从左到右，Box01作为起点，分两条支路，一条经过Box02到Box03，另一条通过虚线到Box04，再隐形关联Box05。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Box01",
        "Box02",
        "Box03",
        "Box04",
        "Box05",
        "LR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，全部设置完成。从左到右布局，四种连线类型都按你说的配好了：箭头实线、普通实线、虚线和隐形连线。",
      "elements_involved": [
